➜湖北诗人木子：七绝·菊 （外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/425375535_100115135	38290
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201017/aa98911080454276a2754a52b8e8a248.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·菊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">菊傲西风一色裁，朵芳香漫蝶难来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天庭若许乾坤转，定与春花一起开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201017/384af9a39965448f8d88c29ded070188.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·枫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烟波淼淼隐丹枫，独揽深秋第一红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎奈西风容不得，无情吹落万山空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201017/52bcb6e8ffa1473a91f157205868043c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
